org.bouncycastle.pqc.asn1

Class GMSSPublicKey

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bouncycastle.asn1.ASN1Object
      • org.bouncycastle.pqc.asn1.GMSSPublicKey
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASN1Encodable, Encodable

    public class GMSSPublicKey
extends ASN1Object
    This class implements an ASN.1 encoded GMSS public key. The ASN.1 definition of this structure is: 
      GMSSPublicKey        ::= SEQUENCE{
      version         INTEGER
      publicKey       OCTET STRING
  }
